    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior paint still holds a beautiful luster, though upon close inspection, you will find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful daily use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with only slight wear visible on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, starts reliably, and shifts smoothly, making it an excellent choice for someone wanting a dependable and attractive vehicle without the premium price of a showroom-perfect model.",
