      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You've found it! I've taken absolute pride in keeping this beauty in tip-top shape\u2014honestly, it\u2019s practically flawless. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner super happy. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
