    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant and a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen is mechanically superlative, featuring a fully documented VANOS bulletproofing and professional rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The naturally aspirated ITBs provide instantaneous throttle response, pulling cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with fresh bushings and M-spec dampers, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque vectoring. Zero oxidation, original VIN tags on all panels, and a comprehensive service history confirm its collector status.",
